<subSubSection id="5DA66552FFCEFFC506F2F8E8FBA9FF32" lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="118" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="150336D9FFCEFFC506F2F8E8FBA9FF32" blockId="6.[151,1437,1643,2030]" lastBlockId="7.[151,1436,151,429]" lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="118" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC406F2F8E8FED2F8BA" bold="true" box="[199,322,1859,1885]" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
This species is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="D2BC4D5AFFCEFFC4045CF8EFFD4BF8B9" authorityName="Cho &amp; Borowiec" authorityYear="2016" box="[617,731,1860,1886]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Gonioctena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fujiana">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC4045CF8EFFDEDF8B9" box="[617,637,1860,1886]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC404B9F8EFFD4BF8B9" box="[652,731,1860,1886]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">fujiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="D2BC4D5AFFCEFFC40521F8EFFC03F8B9" authority="Cho, 2022" authorityName="Cho" authorityYear="2022" box="[788,915,1860,1886]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Gonioctena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jolantae" status="new species">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC40521F8EFFCB8F8B9" box="[788,808,1860,1886]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC40502F8EFFC03F8B9" box="[823,915,1860,1886]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">jolantae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC405AEF8EFFBB5F8BA" bold="true" box="[923,1061,1859,1886]" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="3CFB57B0FFCEFFC405AEF8EFFBB5F8BA" box="[923,1061,1859,1886]" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
in that it has nine black spots on the pronotum and the elytral punctures are arranged in confused single or double rows. However, 
<taxonomicName id="D2BC4D5AFFCEFFC402CBF8C3FA0CF865" authorityName="Chujo DET. M. CHUJO" authorityYear="1958" box="[1278,1436,1896,1922]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Phytodecta" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kamikawai">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC402CBF8C3FA82F865" box="[1278,1298,1896,1922]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC40316F8C3FA0CF865" box="[1315,1436,1896,1922]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">kamikawai</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be distinguished by the following characters: irregular yellowish-brown marking on elytral humerus extending across 1/3–3/5 of elytral base (to 1/2 of base in 
<taxonomicName id="D2BC4D5AFFCEFFC4049BF81BFC8FF82D" authorityName="Cho &amp; Borowiec" authorityYear="2016" box="[686,799,1968,1994]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Gonioctena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fujiana">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC4049BF81BFD52F82D" box="[686,706,1968,1994]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC404E5F81BFC8FF82D" box="[720,799,1968,1994]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">fujiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, to 3/5 of base in 
<taxonomicName id="D2BC4D5AFFCEFFC405DEF81BFBF9F82D" authority="Cho, 2022" authorityName="Cho" authorityYear="2022" box="[1003,1129,1968,1994]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Gonioctena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jolantae" status="new species">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC405DEF81BFC6FF82D" box="[1003,1023,1968,1994]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC40238F81BFBF9F82D" box="[1037,1129,1968,1994]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">jolantae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCEFFC40245F81BFB6AF82E" bold="true" box="[1136,1274,1967,1994]" pageId="6" pageNumber="117">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="3CFB57B0FFCEFFC40245F81BFB6AF82E" box="[1136,1274,1967,1994]" pageId="6" pageNumber="117" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
); median lobe subparallel-sided with apical process narrower than shaft, lateral angles of process distinct (parallel-sided with apical process broader than shaft, lateral angles of process distinct, in 
<taxonomicName id="D2BC4D5AFFCFFFC505B4FF3CFC61FF56" authorityName="Cho &amp; Borowiec" authorityYear="2016" box="[897,1009,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Gonioctena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fujiana">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCFFFC505B4FF3CFC05FF56" box="[897,917,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="118">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCFFFC50597FF3CFC61FF56" box="[930,1009,151,177]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="118">fujiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
; subparallel-sided with apical process narrower than shaft, lateral angles of process rounded, in 
<taxonomicName id="D2BC4D5AFFCFFFC5052FFF10FC08FF32" authority="Cho, 2022" authorityName="Cho" authorityYear="2022" box="[794,920,187,213]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Gonioctena" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="118" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jolantae" status="new species">
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCFFFC5052FFF10FCBEFF32" box="[794,814,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="118">G</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCFFFC50509FF10FC08FF32" box="[828,920,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="118">jolantae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="27C8EACBFFCFFFC505AAFF10FBB8FF33" bold="true" box="[927,1064,186,213]" pageId="7" pageNumber="118">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="3CFB57B0FFCFFFC505AAFF10FBB8FF33" box="[927,1064,186,213]" pageId="7" pageNumber="118" rank="species">new species</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
